WHEN YOU PLAN YOUR TRIP ABROAD-CONSULT THE
PROFESSIONAL EXPERT... YOUR TRAVEL AGENT.
Here are some of the things he can do for you!
HE WILL MAKE YOUR AIR FRANCE RESERVATIONS
He's sure to advise Air France for your
trip abroad because it offers Lockheed
Super Starliner service, convenient and
dependable flights, dreamy French cuisine,
and the ultimate in personal attention.
HELP PLAN YOUR ITINERARY
He'll save you time and money with his vast
store of travel know-how - yours free of
charge. His professional advice will insure
that you do not waste precious travel time,
or incur unnecessary expenses, and that
you make the very most of your trip.
RESERVE YOUR HOTEL ROOMS
Your travel agent knows his hotels throughout
the world. He'll recommend the one best
suited to your budget and plans. Let him
trouble-shoot your reservations problems.
ADVISE ON BAGGAGE AND CLOTHING
He'll explain your air baggage allowance
and the economy of sending your foreign
purchases home via Air France Cargo.
He'll make suggestions about the type of
clothing to carry along, and how to pack it.
HE WILL SUGGEST ALL-EXPENSE TOURS
Complete all-expense Air France vacation
trips at rock-bottom prices are tailored
to your personal preference. A tour will
smooth your way through the complexities
of travel all over the globe.
EXPLAIN FOREIGN EXCHANGE AND INSURANCE
The expert knowledge of your travel agent
can stretch your travel money. He knows
the arrangements to make with your bank
for travellers checks and foreign exchange.
Let him issue the various kinds of insurance
you will want to take out.
DISCUSS SEASONS AND CLIMATE
What's the best time of year to visit the
places you want to go? If you take a
winter vacation this year, where will you
find sun and sand to relax in? Your travel
agent is a mine of information.
MAKE YOUR HOLIDAY FUN
What to see and do ... where to wine and
dine... all this is just a part of your travel
agent's specialized knowledge. Plan with
him the vacation of your dreams, then ..
Bon Voyage ... to a carefree overseas trip
